title: EUR/USD Targets Further Upside Pressure With Eyes On 1.1109 Zone

EUR/USD Targets Further Upside Pressure With Eyes On 1.1109 Zone

FXTechstrategy TeamForex 1 hour ago (Oct 14, 2019 06:23AM ET) By

www.investing.com/analysis/eurusd-targets-further-upside-pressure-with-eyes-on--11109-zone-200472979 EUR/USD Targets Further Upside Pressure With Eyes On 1.1109 Zone By By FXTechstrategy Team | 1 hour ago (Oct 14, 2019 06:23AM ET)

Follow eyes further upside pressure following its second week of strength the past week. Support comes in at the 1.1000 where a break will turn risk to the 1.0950 level. A breach below here will target the 1.0900 level. Further down, support stands at the 1.0850. Conversely, on the upside, resistance comes in at 1.1050 level with a violation of there opening the door for further gain towards the 1.1100 level. Further up, resistance lies at the 1.1150 level. A cut through that level will clear the way for a move towards the 1.1200 level. All in all, EUR/USD expects more gain in the days ahead.
